					<h2>Optimized for Performance</h2>

					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-12">
							<p>SocialSway is a self-service social ad-tech platform. We provide enhanced access to Facebook's native advertising tools. Our proprietary technologies leverage predictive analytics and machine learning to help advertisers gain increased campaign efficiency and significant cost savings.																
							</p>
						</div>						
