							<h4>RESTful API</h4>
							
							<p>Gain access to Time Machine and the rest of our platform's features with an easy to integrate, RESTful API. <br><br> Our API makes it easy to gain the benefits of SocialSway's optimization technologies without the need of learning new software or disrupting workflow. We conform to Facebook's Ads API structure, and advertisers currently accessing Ads API programmatically can seamlessly integrate with SocialSway's API. 
																
						</div>
						<div class = "col-md-4">
							<!-- <img class="img-responsive" src="img/responsiveUX.jpg"> -->
							<%= image_tag("RestfulAPI.jpg", alt: "SocialSway", class: "img-responsive")%>
							
						</div>
					</div>
					
					
							

					<hr class="tall"/>
					
					<div class="row pull-top">
