										</div>
										<div class="feature-box-info">
											<h4 class="shorter">Time Machine</h4>
					 						<p class="tall">Automatically bid the optimal bid type and bid amount during active hours, cutting campaign costs-to-goal up to 20% and decreasing CPAs up to 30%.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class = "col-md-4">
