											<i class="icon icon-dot-circle-o"></i>
										</div>
										<div class="feature-box-info">
											<h4 class="shorter">Goal Optimization</h4>
											<p class="tall">Specify Facebook goals and budgetary constraints at both the Ad Group and Ad Campaign levels. Time Machine optimizes campaigns towards your specific needs.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class = "col-md-4">
