										</div>
										<div class="feature-box-info">
											<h4 class="shorter">Real Time Reporting</h4>
											<p class="tall">Track bidding logic on a real time basis. Built on a clean and simple HTTP request/response system to ensure full compatibility with your current architectures. </p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
									
