							<h4>Budget Reallocation</h4>
							<p class="tall">
								Take full advantage of savings by either using your remaining campaign budget to further boost goals, or re-allocate that campaign budget to other marketing needs. SocialSway can automatically pause campaigns once goals are met so that you can make the choice and maximize your savings.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6">
							<h4>Computational Power</h4>
							<p class="tall">
								Time Machine requires a large amount of computational power to execute in real time. SocialSway's computers are up to the task. We automatically offload all high-performance computing tasks to our servers in order to ensure maximum efficiency, allowing advertisers to concentrate on marketing, not tech.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					
					
					
					<hr class="tall" />
					
					<h4>Enhanced Insights</h4>
					
					<div class = "row">													
