							<p class="tall">
								Leverage analysis done by Time Machine to gain enhanced insights into Ad Groups and Ad Campaigns. <br><br> Gain real time insight into each Ad Group's performance, and gain accurate projections for each Ad Group. Results are provided at a granular level, and broken down by specific action types.<br><br>Track how Time Machine allocates bids in real time, and manage your campaigns knowing which Ad Groups will consume the majority of your budget.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4">
							<!-- <img class="img-responsive" src="img/enhancedInsights.jpg"> -->
